{"tid":18860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁特DQ民主派4議員　葉劉：相信不少市民都撐","createTime":"2016-12-02T13:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T11:25:15.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d95ef59f480003ba001f17bd6961b6ae94fa99","tid":18860,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161202/large/1480683861_d08c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161202%2Flarge%2F1480683861_d08c.jpg&h=87b764b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼青政游蕙禎和梁頌恆後，特首梁振英及律政司司長再入稟高等法院，司法覆核劉小麗、姚松炎、羅冠聰及梁國雄的立法會議員資格，指4人宣誓無效。聲稱獲中央「開綠燈」選特首的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，出席中總酒會後，自稱收到很多市民意見，指不想見到立法會無秩序和做不到事，所以相信政府今次決定，「會得到不少市民支持」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥指離開立法會時，仍未收到任何法庭信件，所以要等立法會秘書處和律師看過後，他才可發表較詳盡的聲明，要求外界「畀啲時間我哋」。"},{"pid":"59da789b5a8ca4aae867a789b30bfe620606c838","tid":18860,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"講還講唔好貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad56d45e4cd080f66fa80f3689a186efff99690","tid":18860,"uid":43597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"人無恥則無敵"},{"pid":"9d5d8e7540f42108d1d1500e029503c08b398674","tid":18860,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"事實係咁，你試下落茶餐廳問下d阿叔阿伯，掃把頭邊有講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310cdcf33a97008d6c4d13ed07b7034a4df6f102","tid":18860,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"我撐你老母落海就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d246d93c1bce5755dd55fd5b6776a0a4955af4","tid":18860,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"撐你孽瘤全家做雞做公廁比狗屌呀<img src=\"/assets/fac